# Portfolio Website — Walkthrough (v2)

## Project Structure

```
Portofolio Website/
├── src/
│   ├── data/portfolio.json      ← Editable content
│   ├── pages/index.astro        ← Main page with all sections + JS
│   └── styles/global.css        ← CSS with dark mode + animations
├── netlify.toml                 ← Netlify deploy config
└── package.json
```

## Enhancements Added

### 🌙 Dark Mode
- **Auto-detection**: Checks `prefers-color-scheme` on first visit
- **Toggle button**: In navbar (both desktop and mobile). Moon ↔ Sun icon
- **Persistence**: Saves preference to `localStorage`
- **Anti-FOUC**: Inline `<script>` in `<head>` applies dark class before first paint
- All colors use CSS variables that swap between light/dark

### ✨ Scroll Reveal Animations
4 animation types, all using `IntersectionObserver`:
- **reveal** — fade-in-up (default)
- **reveal-left / reveal-right** — slide from sides (used on timeline cards)
- **reveal-scale** — scale-up fade (used on hero image)
- **reveal-stagger** — parent class that auto-staggers children with delays

### 🎨 Decorative Elements
- Floating geometric shapes (rings, dots, crosses) in Hero, Work, and Timeline sections
- Grid pattern overlay on stats bar
- Section connector dots between major sections
- Floating badges on hero image ("Open to Work", "Since 2019")

### 📊 New Sections
- **Stats bar** — 50+ Projects, 3+ Years, 2 Companies, 100% Passion (counters animate on scroll)
- **Skills marquee** — Auto-scrolling carousel of skill tags with icons
- **Footer CTA card** — Gradient "Let's Work Together" card with glowing animation

### 🔄 Micro-Animations
- Typing cursor blink after hero name
- Pulse glow on timeline dots
- Button shimmer on hover
- Image zoom on card hover
- Magnetic hover on social icons
- Nav link underline draw on hover
- Float bounce on hero badges
- Shimmer loading placeholder for images

