## Deployment

```bash
npm run build    # → dist/
# Push to GitHub → Netlify auto-deploys via netlify.toml
```

> [!NOTE]
> Replace placeholder images in [portfolio.json](file:///d:/WORK/Everlenss/Portofolio%20Website/src/data/portfolio.json) with actual portfolio images. Update social links and email in [index.astro](file:///d:/WORK/Everlenss/Portofolio%20Website/src/pages/index.astro).
